After downloading the repo, follow this steps:

1) Open two terminal and reach to the file location in both of them.
2) On one terminal, type 'npm install' (to download the essential JavaScript libraries or development tools locally to your machine (dictated by our package.json file))
3) Once that is done; open the other window and run the python file (app.py)
4) Once you get that, open our terminal of Step-2 and run the frontend by typing 'npm start'
5) It will take some time to run depending on the size of the dataset.
6) Once that's set, you are good to go!!
7) Click on the 'Initiate Telemetry' button and enjoy the graphs
